Eddie Nartey (a mụrụ na 6 Nọvemba 1984) bụ onye Ghana na-eme ihe nkiri, onye nduzi, na onye na-emepụta ihe nkiri. Ọrụ nkwado ya na Frank Rajah's Somewhere In Africa mere ka a họpụta ya na Nollywood na African Film Critics Awards (NAFCA), na onyinye ihe nkiri Ghana. A họpụtara ya na ngalaba onye na-eme ihe nkiri kachasị mma maka Kiss Me If You Can., O nwetara ohere mbụ ya ime ihe nkiri izizi ya nke akpọrọ Could This Be Love ebe ya na Evelyn dere ihe nkiri ahụ, nke ndị na-eme ihe nkiri dịka Majid Michel, Kwadwo Nkansah (Lil Win), Nana Ama Mcbrown, Fred Amugi, na Gloria Sarfo.
Ya na Juliet Ibrahim rụkọrọ ọrụ na ihe nkiri Shattered Romance
O dekwara ma duzie ihe nkiri Royal Diadem
O nwere njikọ na British Actor / Director Danny Erskine
Eddie gara Korle Gonno Methodist primary na JSS na Accra maka agụmakwụkwọ bụ isi
Agụmakwụkwọ sekọndrị ya bịara na Holy Trinity Cathedral Secondary School (HOTCASS)
Ọ gara Mahadum nke Ghana, Legon ebe ọ gụrụ maka iduzi ma nweta BFA na Fine Arts.
Nwunye ya nwụrụ na Jenụwarị afọ 2021 mgbe afọ abụọ nke alụmdi na nwunye gasịrị.
